{"tid":1450452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聽日入定唔入？」用正負評話比打工仔知 聽朝起身有冇人同佢地一齊罷工入機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:25:08.000Z","uid":4036,"like":74,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ca834886fb2f227d551cb580defaeae78d17f3d6","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:37:05.000Z","msg":"身為一個打工仔，我諗有好多人罷工要都付出一定嘅代價，但作為一個打工仔之前，我地都係熱愛香港嘅香港人，見到721件事以為已經好大件事，點知今日811完全係警察鄉黑聯手，真心係嬲到訓唔著，好想有d野係自己可以做。<br />\n<br />\n我公司有好多人收到whatspp group 呀 ig呀 連登宣傳話聽日罷工， 而佢地都想幫手，但奈可罷工代價大，二來連登出現兩種風向，一個係即時罷工，聽日就入機場；另一個係準備好，宣傳好再一炮過入去。<br />\n<br />\n兩個post都好多正評同好多回覆，令好多打工仔（包括我）都唔知聽日罷唔罷好，講真罷工代價係大，但發生咗811咗嘅事，我願意付出呢個代價去幫香港出一分力，但起碼打工打會想知道，到底聽日罷唔罷好，會唔會自己罷咗原來最後係冇行動。<br />\n<br />\n正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：用行動去文宣，學生先全面進場，可以聽日罷工嘅人齊入去。其他人想幫手但罷唔切工，可以簡星期二黎接力同埋帶物資入黎，務求令機場塞滿人。<br />\n<br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：太急太多事發生，宣傳唔切，要比多d時間文宣做野，應該簡一日再宣傳。"},{"pid":"0fe8d1726eee34247842cf3f0b0349b024585ffc","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:38:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d77f4afebbd35c862747b74000c27b6d7e24936","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a20d04365413bbcbfbe72ae21af78e54e315a10e","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果真係驚宣傳唔切，其實只要聽朝去塞鐵，打工仔已經大條道理罷工。"},{"pid":"ca53d56c092cb6117ad5ff2401d4ddd5509de1cc","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:28.000Z","msg":"十連push"},{"pid":"f57da76fe1838dd63d0a5764303c349a8ae823e3","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:41:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3273708cd033e395e1673021329187eebaab1e23","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a4302358e73b4ea7a6b6d73d168d7b5f394bd68","tid":1450452,"uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"聽日唔好太急， 唔係塞交通時候，唔係比人錯左焦點"},{"pid":"13357f4ddb48f10e6a87896cfb78ad2ec4170a01","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66cf9e812693ce93bd3820febc7564194cdb9dff","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9cfd5c3d13581ff6b3a403206f5a0a14a8c003b3","tid":1450452,"uid":222722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:47:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4423db971967fae7abfb7eae64648d9ff9b14c80","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d67bdc6d319aa4225345a6e45b29f44399a681b3","tid":1450452,"uid":36920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a4302358e73b4ea7a6b6d73d168d7b5f394bd68","tid":1450452,"uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"聽日唔好太急， 唔係塞交通時候，唔係比人錯左焦點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:03:54.000Z","msg":"諗諗今晚發生咩事"},{"pid":"3a3868afd4c0ae1eab47d437506608a82b4cae2a","tid":1450452,"uid":4036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d67bdc6d319aa4225345a6e45b29f44399a681b3","tid":1450452,"uid":36920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a4302358e73b4ea7a6b6d73d168d7b5f394bd68","tid":1450452,"uid":267942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:42:54.000Z","msg":"聽日唔好太急， 唔係塞交通時候，唔係比人錯左焦點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019